---
title: Malay Lamb Curry with Cheat's Chapatis
description: This flavoursome Lamb Curry with Chapatis is deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/malay-lamb-curry-1a6cc552-ac7907fd.jpg
